      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay. May I help you?",
      "zh": "好的。需要幫忙嗎？",
      "ja": "はい。いかがなさいますか？",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How much is it? It's $5.",
      "zh": "多少錢？是5美元。",
      "ja": "いくらですか？5ドルです。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want this hat. How much is it?",
      "zh": "我想要這頂帽子。多少錢？",
      "ja": "この帽子が欲しいです。いくらですか？",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's $10.",
      "zh": "是10美元。",
      "ja": "10ドルです。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sally, you look very pretty.",
      "zh": "莎莉，你看起來很漂亮。",
      "ja": "サリー、とてもきれいだね。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Dad.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，爸爸。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、お父さん。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now, let's have lunch.",
      "zh": "現在，我們去吃午餐吧。",
      "ja": "さあ、お昼ご飯にしましょう。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's role play.",
